duties_responsibilities.duty: Coordinating transactions and writing contracts to facilitate smooth real estate deals.

Setting up investor consultations to understand their needs and preferences.
Assist in generating compelling marketing materials to showcase our properties effectively.
Assisting with additional tasks as required to support the growth of the company.
